## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most current research or guidelines. The classification of diabetics as clinically vulnerable can vary by region and specific health guidelines, which may not be fully captured in this report. Additionally, individual risk factors and comorbidities play a significant role in determining clinical vulnerability, which requires personalized medical assessment.